headline: This AI Startup Could Be Next In Palo Alto Networks Acquisition Playbook
summary: Palo Alto stock dipped amid a report the cybersecurity firm may acquire artificial intelligence startup ProtectAI for around $650 million.

headline: HSBC upgrades Palo Alto amid rise in cyber threats, valuation ease
summary: Investing.com -- HSBC upgraded Palo Alto Networks (NASDAQ:PANW) to “Hold” from “Reduce,” citing resilient cybersecurity demand in the face of macroeconomic uncertainty and a valuation that is no longer stretched.
